SpoonerPlacements.Note: Split-second decisions can be difficult when you're strapped into the lovechild of a supercar and a space shuttle. And trust us, which turbo-charged loop to take off the start line is just the beginning of this dilemma. Throw in a tightly-wound stunt plane and a herd of pocket-sized helicopters, and your multitasking better be up to scratch. Lap Transform Race starting in the Rocket Voltic, also featuring the Mallard, Havok and Motorcycles.
